author: Linda Givetash and Gabe Gutierrez and Matthew Johnson and Leou Chen
title: New York State now has more reported coronavirus cases than any country
description: The number of confirmed coronavirus cases in New York has reached 151,598, according to NBC News' tracking, outpacing any country except the United States.
